<DATELINE>BEIT UMMAR, Occupied West Bank (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Half the Arab policemen in
the West Bank resigned by PLO order Friday and Israeli soldiers
closed the main Gaza mosque on the Moslem sabbath for the first
time worshipers could remember.
   The Al Amari mosque in Gaza City has been a rallying point for
