<TEXT>
   Investor Burt Sugarman says two
companies he controls had boosted their stake in Media General Inc.
to 10 percent from 9.8 percent and would seek a shareholder vote on
his $1.75 billion takeover offer.
   However, Virginia-based Media General disputed Sugarman's
contentions Thursday on how the company's two classifications of
stock would be allowed to vote on a merger.
